title: The Masters Of The Universe RPG
description:
The Masters Of The Universe Role Playing Game

Copyright 1985 FASA Corp. under license from Mattel, Inc.
Game Design: Ross Babcock
Written By: Jack C. Harris
Drawn By: Hillary Barta, Doug Rice, Willie Schubert, Rick Taylor (First Comics)
Edited By: Mike Gold

Contents:
The 24 page illustrated rulebook in B&W. ..and the &#039;Oops!&#039; sheet from FASA.
All of the original full-color counters, ready to print out on card stock.
The original &#039;Catacombs of Snake Mountain&#039; game board in full resolution!
The only thing you&#039;ll need is two six-sided dice.
